==幕后==
该剧里，黄圣依和秦丽出演的女角色爱上了同一个男人，上演“[[三角恋|三角恋]]”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pic.news.sohu.com/group-225426.shtml#g=225426&p=2022594 |title=《广府太极传奇》热播 黄圣依秦丽成姐妹花 |work=搜狐网 |date=2014-04-04 |access-date=2014-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407100726/http://pic.news.sohu.com/group-225426.shtml#g=225426&p=2022594 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2011年，该剧荣获“[[五个一工程|五个一工程]]”奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.he.xinhuanet.com/zfwq/2011-07/06/content_23175592.htm|title=《广府太极传奇》获省“五个一”工程奖|work=新华网|date=2011-07-06|accessdate=2014-04-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407100722/http://www.he.xinhuanet.com/zfwq/2011-07/06/content_23175592.htm|archivedate=2014-04-07}}</ref>

该剧播出之后，催发了广府的旅游热。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.china.com.cn/rollnews/2010-08/02/content_3566317.htm |title=《广府太极传奇》催热广府旅游 |work=中国网 |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2014-04-04 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407075928/http://news.china.com.cn/rollnews/2010-08/02/content_3566317.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

